*SCREAM* I DON&quot;T WANT TO NURF ANOTHER CLASS DAMN IT, I WANT VERANT TO THINK AHEAD.<br>
<br>
There, i've said it.  WTF came up with the idea that the best way to deal with a screwing is to accept the screwing then scream for everyone else to be screwed harder?<br>
<br>
I half feel that the reason for all these classes being out of balance right now is because all we've done as a community (EQ community, not Monk community) is scream for everyone else to be DECREASED BELOW US...not to have us increased above them.<br>
<br>
Jesus people, this is lowest comon denominator thinking.  I'm stupid and you should be too so we can all be the same.  How about if you're stupid we bring you up with the smart people and BETTER ourselves, instead of constantly nurfing ourselves.<br>
<br>
How the HELL did we all get into the concept that because we are suffering we should do our damndest to inflict pain and suffering onto others to make it right.  How does that make it right?<br>
<br>
LEAVE THE OTHER CLASSES ALONE.  If there's a problem with your class WORK WITH VERANT AS A COMMUNITY to INCREASE your class to make it right. <p>Tsarakien Roycroft<br>
